description: Sunday’s tornadoes near Beauregard struck an area that rarely sees such strong storms.
title: Alabama Tornado Among the Region’s Worst in 30 Years
title_page: Alabama Tornado Among the Region’s Worst in 30 Years - The New York Times
maintext: The devastating milewide tornado that flattened parts of rural Alabama on Sunday and killed at least 23 people was the worst the state had seen in years.
